                    <p><code class="bg-gray-200 px-1 rounded">ANTHROPIC_API_KEY</code> - Anthropic API 密钥</p>
                    <p><code class="bg-gray-200 px-1 rounded">ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL</code> - API 基础 URL（可选）</p>
                    <p><code class="bg-gray-200 px-1 rounded">ANTHROPIC_MODEL</code> - 模型名称（可选）</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 底部按钮 -->
